articles.title: Macron: ‘Emily in Paris’ must stay in Paris - POLITICO Europe
articles.description: Hit show wouldn’t “make sense” in Rome, the French president told Variety.
articles.content: The show is one of Netflix’s biggest hits and was recently picked up for a fifth season. While it is reviled by some Parisians for its stereotypical depiction of the French capital angry locals have … [+572 chars]
